Careers at sbe


WELCOMEsbe is proud to be the pioneer in the hospitality industry.

sbe is not like other employers. We are fun, authentic,
gracious and passionate and offer a work environment that both reflects our unique
culture and instills our core values. sbe takes pride in creating a
guest experience that is original, memorable and totally one-of-a kind. This
same dynamic experience inspires each and every sbe employee.  

Founded in New York City in 1984, Morgans Hotel Group was the world-renowned originator of the boutique hotel
concept.

By constantly looking to the future and actively reinventing the hotel experience , sbe has created breakthrough concepts that have revolutionized
the hospitality industry. In fact, the very term "boutique hotel" was
coined to describe our first hotel on Madison Avenue, Morgans. Our
design-driven approach to reinventing the traditional hotel space has made sbe a sought after brand for guests and owners alike. 

After being acquired by sbe in 2016, the future for Morgans Hotel Group promises continued domestic
and international growth. As the creator of iconic brands such as Delano
and Mondrian, our hotels are located in key gateway cities around the world,
including Las Vegas, Los Angeles, New York, San Francisco, South Beach,
Istanbul, London, and soon Doha, Qatar.  Explore how you can be a part of a winning team with a driving
purpose to create engaging and dynamic guest experiences within sbe. 






