	Cancellation policies vary by hotel and destination. Please see below for
	your hotel’s cancellation policy.
Los Angeles
	Mondrian
	Cancellations must be made before 6:00 PM 24 hours prior to arrival to avoid
	a charge of one night’s room and tax fees. An early departure fee of $100 will
	be charged if guests check out prior to their departure date. Policies can vary
	for specials, packages, and prepaid reservations. Please review the booking
	description of your reservation.
New York
	Hudson, Morgans, Royalton
	Cancellations must be made before 6:00 PM 24 hours prior to arrival to avoid
	a charge of one night’s room and tax fees. An early departure fee of $50 will
	be charged if guests check out prior to their departure date. Policies can vary
	for specials, packages, and prepaid reservations. Please review the booking
	description of your reservation.
San Francisco
	Clift
	Cancellations must be made before 6:00 PM 24 hours prior to arrival to avoid
	a charge of one night’s room and tax fees. An early departure fee of $75 will
	be charged if guests check out prior to their departure date. Policies can vary
	for specials, packages, and prepaid reservations. Please review the booking
	description of your reservation.
South Beach
	Delano, Mondrian, Shore Club
	Cancellations must be made before 4:00 pm three days prior to arrival to
	avoid a charge of one night’s room and tax fees. A one night deposit fee will
	be taken at time of booking, if reservation is cancelled and cancellation
	policy is met, the one night deposit will be refunded. For arrivals January 2,
	2017 through April 15, 2017 one night deposit and seven day cancellation
	required. For arrivals November 27, 2016 through December 4, 2016 and arrivals
	December 26, 2016 through January 2, 2017 full deposit and 30 day
	cancellation required. An early departure fee of 1 night stay and tax will be charged if guests
	check out prior to their departure date. Specific policies may apply.


Deposits & Guarantees
	A credit card is required at the time of booking to guarantee the room. All
	Miami resorts require a one day deposit at time of booking. Special event
	periods may require an actual deposit depending on the time of booking and will
	be stated during the booking process. Direct billing accounts must be set up
	through Property Accounting Offices and guests must fax requests on company
	letterhead.
London
Mondrian London at Sea Containers, Sanderson, and St Martins Lane
	Cancellations must be made before 6:00 PM 24 hours prior to arrival to avoid a charge of one night’s room and tax fees. An early departure fee of £50 will be charged if guests check out prior to their departure date. Policies can vary for specials, packages, and prepaid reservations. Please review the booking description of your reservation.Check-In/Check-Out
	Delano South Beach:
	Check-In time is 4pm. Check-Out time is 11am.
	Mondrian, Clift, Hudson, Morgans, Royalton, Sanderson, St Martins Lane, and Shore Club:
	Check-In time is 3pm. Check-Out time is 12pm. Early Check-In is by request only and not guaranteed. A valid credit card must be presented at Check-In at all hotels.  Late Check-Out must be coordinated with the hotel if it is available. Guests must be at least 21 years old to check into a hotel, with the following exceptions.  In London, at Mondrian London at Sea Containers, Sanderson, and St Martins Lane guests must be 18 with valid I.D. to check in.  In the state of California, at Mondrian Los Angeles and Clift, minors are permitted to check-in with a written or electronic form from a parent, guardian or responsible adult assuming liability for charges, obligations, injuries and/or damages relating to the minor’s stay.  In the state of Florida, the minimum age is waived for individuals with a valid I.D. who are currently on active duty as a member of the US Armed Forces, National Guard, Reserve Forces or Coast Guard.  Parking
Los Angeles
Mondrian Los Angeles- Valet parking is available 24 hours a day at the main entrance of Mondrian on Sunset Blvd roughly 0.1 mile east of La Cienega Blvd. You will find the entrance to the drive located just before the historical Monument Doors. $44 per night.  Vehicles may be taken in and out.  Please allow 10 minutes for vehicle retrieval.
New York
	Hudson- Valet parking is available 24 hours a day at our main entrance on 58th street.  $65 per night.  Vehicles may not be taken in and out.  Please allow 15 minutes for vehicle retrieval.
Morgans- Valet parking is available 24 hours a day at our main entrance on the east side of Madison Avenue between 36th and 37th streets. Standard Vehicle $55 plus tax per night; Oversize Vehicle / SUV $65 plus tax per night.  Vehicles may not be taken in and out.  Please allow 15 minutes for vehicle retrieval.
	Royalton- Valet parking is available 24 hours a day at the main entrance at 44 W. 44th St.  Standard vehicles $56 plus tax per night; Oversize Vehicle / SUV $66 plus tax per night.  Vehicles may not be taken in and out.  Please allow 30 minutes for vehicle retrieval.
San Francisco
Clift - Valet Parking is available 24 hours a day at the main entrance at 495 Geary St. between Mason and Taylor.  Standard Vehicle $58 plus 14% tax per night; Oversize Vehicle $69 plus 14% tax per night. Vehicles may be taken in and out. Please allow 20 minutes for vehicle retrieval.
South Beach
Delano - Valet parking is available at our main entrance on Collins Ave, 24 hours a day. $42 per night. Vehicles may be taken in and out. $26 for visits up to 4 hours or $15 with restaurant or spa validation. Please allow 10 minutes for vehicle retrieval.
	Mondrian South Beach- Valet parking is available 24 hours a day at our main entrance on 11th St. and West Avenue. $41 per night. Vehicles may be taken in and out. Please allow 10 minutes for vehicle retrieval.
	Shore Club - Valet parking is available at our main entrance on Collins Ave, 24 hours a day. $42 per night. Vehicles may be taken in and out. Please allow 10 minutes for vehicle retrieval.
Istanbul
	10 Karaköy- Valet parking is available at the main entrance on Kemeralti Street 24 hours a day. Parking fee is TL 20,- per night.
LondonMondrian London – There are limited valet parking facilities at an additional £45 for overnight parking or £30 for up to 6 hours, subject to availability on the day. Vehicles may be taken in and out.  Please allow 10 minutes for vehicle retrieval.
	Sanderson - Valet parking is available at the main entrance on Berners Street, 24 hours a day. The entrance to the car park is on Wells Mews. £45 per night. Vehicles may be taken in and out. Please allow 10 minutes for vehicle retrieval.
	St Martins Lane - Valet parking is available at the main entrance on 45 St Martins Lane, 24 hours a day (£5 valet parking per transfer). The entrance to the car park is on Bedfordbury. £40 per night. Vehicles may be taken in and out. Please allow 10 minutes for vehicle retrieval.Pets
	All Morgans Hotel Group hotels are pet friendly. 
	The animal must weigh 20
	pounds or less, a 
	contract/waiver must be signed upon arrival and a $100/UK£100 non-refundable deposit is required (Shore Club - $200 refundable). No pets are allowed in restaurants or
	bars, by the pool or beach, and may 
	not be left unattended in the guest rooms.
San Francisco
Clift - There is no deposit charged. A pet
 indemnity form must be filled out at the front desk when checking into the hotel. An additional cleaning fee may be applied after check-out, if 
necessary.

