Is This your Company?














Morgans Hotel Group Co Overview



Website:

www.morganshotelgroup.com

Locations:


                                                             New York, NY 

                                                

Employees:
1,790




Founded:
N/A
CEO:
W Edward Scheetz
Industry:

Hotels And Motels



Revenue:
$252,538,530





                                            Morgans Hotel Group Co, whose headquarters are located at New York, NY, is a hotel. It pulls in a yearly revenue of $252.5 million and employs 1,790 people. Though Morgans Hotel Group Co has yet to hit the mainstream, it's found niche success. The firm is currently headed by CEO W Edward Scheetz.
                                        









